A man has been charged with the attempted murder of an 18-year-old woman who was stabbed.She was attacked at a property in Albert Road, Southport, at about 17:20 BST on Saturday, Merseyside Police said.The force added that she was in a "a stable condition" in hospital.A 38-year-old male, of Albert Road,  will appear later at Liverpool Magistrates' Court.
